@davidi2 wrote:

[quote=“TimmahPwnz, post:3, topic:376842”]Hmm, I always thought sendQuest was for like the quest tab, not because of the “Quest” part of the void lol, but the quest tab is an interface, so I’m going in circles and I’m not sure what to do D: ?[/quote]You would use setString(“Quest”, questtabid, id);

basically the same as sendQuest, but you have to add the quest tab interface id.
